videos.description: Alex Hornibrook throws an interception right to Coney Durr deep in Minnesota territory.
videos.headline: Minnesota intercepts Hornibrook deep in own territory

videos.description: Mohamed Ibrahim runs for a 10-yard touchdown on 4th down to give Minnesota a 10-0 lead.
videos.headline: Ibrahim finds corner on 4th-down TD run

videos.description: Alex Hornibrook throws a 7-yard touchdown in the closing seconds of the half as nuns celebrate on sideline.
videos.headline: Badgers fans blessed as Wisconsin finds end zone

videos.description: Wisconsin's Alex Hornibrook throws into heavy coverage for his second interception of the game.
videos.headline: Hornibrook throws costly pick near midfield

videos.description: Bryce Williams runs for a 23-yard touchdown to put the game on ice for Minnesota on the first play after a strip sack by the defense.
videos.headline: Gophers score one play after strip sack
